item.title: CVE-2019-15708|2024-08-05T00:56:22.305Z -- fortinet -- fortinet%20fortiap-s%2Fw2
item.description: A system command injection vulnerability in the FortiAP-S/W2 6.2.1, 6.2.0, 6.0.5 and below, FortiAP 6.0.5 and below and FortiAP-U below 6.0.0 under CLI admin console may allow unauthorized administrators to run arbitrary system level commands via specially crafted ifconfig commands.
